KeyManager
----------
Link HW
Event keyboard -> Token (event)
'a' -> EVENT_LEFT
'a' -> EVENT_CHAR_A


InputProcessor
--------------
Submit current events to the EventManagers
for every event e
  for every EventManagers EM do
    if EM->process(e)
       break


EventManager
------------
Abstract class ?
process(event)
List of processable events


State
-----
Has an EventManager


